sql:
SELECT type_name, race_type_distance_range
FROM race_types
WHERE type_id = 1;

SELECT TANH(average_finishing_position)
FROM trainer_performance
WHERE trainer_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
- "standout trainers" refers to trainers whose performance metrics exceed the average; 
- "success rates" includes win and place percentages;
- "the latter part of last year" refers to October 2022;
- "above the norm" means having win and place percentages greater than the calculated average for all trainers.

sql:
SELECT AVG(win_percentage) AS AverageWinPercentage
FROM trainer_performance
WHERE wins > 0;

SELECT COUNT(trainer_id) 
FROM trainers 
WHERE trainer_rank = 'National Champion';

SELECT trainers.trainer_name, horses.horse_name, horses.horse_career_earnings
FROM horses
JOIN trainers ON horses.trainer_id = trainers.trainer_id
WHERE horses.horse_career_earnings = (
    SELECT MIN(horse_career_earnings) FROM horses
);

external_knowledge:
- Prize money formatted with commas is excluded from the total earnings calculation because it represents a different currency format or erroneous data;
- 'Average earnings per race' is a common metric in competitive racing contexts to evaluate trainer performance;
- 'No race data' indicates that the trainer has not participated in any races, leading to an undefined average earnings value.

sql:
SELECT trainer_name, trainer_experience_years
FROM trainers
ORDER BY trainer_experience_years DESC;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT trainer_id)
FROM trainer_performance
WHERE g1_wins > 0 OR g2_wins > 0 OR g3_wins > 0 OR lr_wins > 0;
